{# IRS-VERIFIED 2026-05-11 — chain on 2025 Schedule 2 PDF
   https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/f1040s2.pdf #}
The AMT amount is entered on [Form 6251](https://www.irs.gov/forms-pubs/about-form-6251) line 11, which the IRS instructs you to carry to **[Schedule 2](https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/f1040s2.pdf) line 2** (the 2025 revision moved AMT from line 1 to line 2). Schedule 2 line 3 then totals line 1z (additions to tax — APTC repayment, clean-vehicle credit repayments, Form 4255 EPE recapture) and line 2 (AMT); for the supported posture line 1z is $0, so Schedule 2 line 3 = the AMT above. Schedule 2 line 3 carries to **[Form 1040](https://www.irs.gov/forms-pubs/about-form-1040) line 17**.

